Captains Log:We are close to the planet where we got the distress 
call we entered the galaxy early this morning.I notice that there are 
many differences of this galaxy then ours.There looks like there is 
alot of debri in the space as well.I should go check on my crew now.
Just then....Boom.
What was that ohh shit we're bein pulled into the atmosphere of this 
strange planet.We're going to fast we're gonna crash.
Over Intercom:Guys get ready for impact and hold on to something.The 
landings going to be rough.
They speed through the atmosphere crashing on what is now known as 
the continent of Australia.The ship continues forward for some time 
till eventually the ship stops abruptly.
Super Fire Convoy(u can call him SFC for short):Crew status report.Is 
everyone ok?
God Magnus:Sir I'm ok.Tat was a rough crash we should check the ship 
and its damage.
SFC:I'm very aware of that God Magnus but thanks anyways.
